00:01:48.800 --> 00:01:54.080
[Amit Varma]: His account in the book is surprisingly balanced and has personal touches that I found refreshing

00:01:54.080 --> 00:01:54.640
[Amit Varma]: for example

00:01:54.640 --> 00:02:02.040
[Amit Varma]: He writes that he liked much that was in the BJP manifesto of 2014 and that he was hopeful that Modi would fulfill some of

00:02:02.040 --> 00:02:06.440
[Amit Varma]: His promises. In fact, his book is called the great disappointment

00:02:06.760 --> 00:02:11.200
[Amit Varma]: Because Modi did not fulfill those promises when I wrote to Salman to invite him for the show

00:02:11.200 --> 00:02:17.280
[Amit Varma]: I told him that I wanted to talk about more than just what was in the book many of the topics he covers like

00:02:17.280 --> 00:02:23.720
