00:02:35.680 --> 00:02:42.320
[Amit Varma]: Ask me anything and indeed he gamely took on everything. I threw at him. He told me what the UPA did wrong

00:02:42.320 --> 00:02:44.200
[Amit Varma]: He explained what Modi got right?

00:02:44.200 --> 00:02:51.480
