00:02:52.200 --> 00:02:54.680
[Amit Varma]: Whether his answers convinced you or not is a different matter

00:02:54.680 --> 00:02:57.720
[Amit Varma]: but I was enormously impressed at the sincerity and the

00:02:57.880 --> 00:03:06.040
