[Guest]: I don't think we can come out of this anytime soon if it continues this way. I'm not

01:05:40.380 --> 01:05:44.300
[Guest]: Confident that this is going to increase. Uh, I don't think this is going to be good for the country

01:05:44.300 --> 01:05:46.300
[Guest]: Frankly if they continue with this structure

01:05:46.860 --> 01:05:51.100
[Guest]: Uh, this is a crazy structure. It needs to be disbanded or abandoned

01:05:51.660 --> 01:05:56.460
