01:05:56.460 --> 01:05:59.580
[Guest]: Uh reforming it. They just abandoned it

01:06:00.460 --> 01:06:06.220
[Guest]: It's a very you know, you have a country that is so diverse and then suddenly you're trying to you know

01:06:06.780 --> 01:06:09.820
[Guest]: Reform the system and you try to do it in one fell swoop

01:06:10.380 --> 01:06:16.220
[Guest]: And without any planning without any proper planning preparation, you'll have a disaster. That's what happened

